Package: icare
Type: Package
Title: Intelligent ClinlAbomics Research Expedition
Version: 0.1.3
Author: User
Maintainer: User <user@example.com>
Description: A modular framework for clinical statistics, missing-data
    handling, feature selection, machine learning, unsupervised subtyping
    (clustering, NMF, latent profile analysis), and prognostic / survival
    modeling for clinical and omics data. Provides utilities for descriptive
    statistics, model benchmarking and explanation, nomogram and decision
    curve analysis, and interactive Shiny dashboards for model deployment.
License: GPL-3
